SMITH, Respondent, v. MILLIKEN et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by John J. Smith against Nathan J. Milliken and Charles F. Milliken.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Interlocutory judgment appealed from affirmed, with costs, with leave to the defendants to withdraw demurrer, and answer over within 20 days, on payment of the costs of this appeal and of the demurrer.
